author: KEXP
description: London-based trio @mary-inthejunkyard arrive with bewitching and emotive experimental rock goodness. In-studio with host DJ Cheryl Waters, the band share a moody performance of "Tuesday" and more across their discography.
title: mary in the junkyard peform "Tuesday" & more Live on KEXP
